      Sample dishes confirmation: You agreed to offer the photographer and writer some sample dishes for them to taste, write about and take photos of.
    %li
      No charge confirmation: You agreed to not charge the photographer or writer for any of the sample dishes or drinks that they receive when they go to your restaurant.


